---
---

<div class="mt-8">
    <div class="group relative bg-gradient-to-br from-zinc-800/40 to-zinc-900/40 backdrop-blur-sm border border-purple-500/30 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 hover:border-purple-500/50 transition-all duration-500 shadow-xl hover:shadow-purple-500/10 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500/5 to-transparent rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>

        <div class="absolute top-10 right-10 w-32 h-32 bg-purple-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse-slow"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-10 w-40 h-40 bg-violet-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse-slower"></div>

        <div class="relative flex items-start gap-6 mb-8">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500/10 to-purple-600/10 border border-purple-500/20 p-4 rounded-xl group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:border-purple-500/40 transition-all duration-300">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white group-hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors duration-300">
                        GL Studios
                    </h3>
                    <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-500/20 border border-purple-500/30 rounded-full text-xs font-bold text-purple-300">
                        Mi Studio
                    </span>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-5">
                    <p class="text-lg text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
                        GL Studios es mi estudio de desarrollo donde trabajo principalmente en la <span class="text-purple-400 font-bold">creación de plugins y mods para Minecraft</span>. Ofrecemos servicios profesionales adaptados a las necesidades específicas de cada cliente.
                    </p>
                    <div class="bg-zinc-800/50 border-l-4 border-purple-500 p-4 rounded-r-lg">
                        <p class="text-base text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed italic">
                            Realizamos <span class="text-purple-400 font-bold">comisiones personalizadas</span> ajustadas a cada persona o servidor, garantizando <span class="text-white font-semibold">calidad, eficiencia y soporte continuo</span> en todos nuestros proyectos.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-purple-500/5 border border-purple-500/20 rounded-lg">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-300">
                            <span class="font-bold text-purple-400">Servicios:</span> Desarrollo de plugins personalizados, mods de Minecraft, configuración de servidores y soluciones a medida para comunidades gaming.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-8">
            <a
                href="https://discord.glstudios.dev"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="group/link relative bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-purple-600 hover:from-purple-600 hover:to-violet-700 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg shadow-purple-500/30 hover:shadow-purple-500/50 hover:scale-105 overflow-hidden flex items-center gap-2"
            >
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M20.317 4.37a19.791 19.791 0 00-4.885-1.515.074.074 0 00-.079.037c-.21.375-.444.864-.608 1.25a18.27 18.27 0 00-5.487 0 12.64 12.64 0 00-.617-1.25.077.077 0 00-.079-.037A19.736 19.736 0 003.677 4.37a.07.07 0 00-.032.027C.533 9.046-.32 13.58.099 18.057a.082.082 0 00.031.057 19.9 19.9 0 005.993 3.03.078.078 0 00.084-.028c.462-.63.874-1.295 1.226-1.994a.076.076 0 00-.041-.106 13.107 13.107 0 01-1.872-.892.077.077 0 01-.008-.128 10.2 10.2 0 00.372-.292.074.074 0 01.077-.01c3.928 1.793 8.18 1.793 12.062 0a.074.074 0 01.078.01c.12.098.246.198.373.292a.077.077 0 01-.006.127 12.299 12.299 0 01-1.873.892.077.077 0 00-.041.107c.36.698.772 1.362 1.225 1.993a.076.076 0 00.084.028 19.839 19.839 0 006.002-3.03.077.077 0 00.032-.054c.5-5.177-.838-9.674-3.549-13.66a.061.061 0 00-.031-.03zM8.02 15.33c-1.183 0-2.157-1.085-2.157-2.419 0-1.333.956-2.419 2.157-2.419 1.21 0 2.176 1.096 2.157 2.42 0 1.333-.956 2.418-2.157 2.418zm7.975 0c-1.183 0-2.157-1.085-2.157-2.419 0-1.333.955-2.419 2.157-2.419 1.21 0 2.176 1.096 2.157 2.42 0 1.333-.946 2.418-2.157 2.418z"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="relative z-10">Únete al Discord</span>
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-violet-600 opacity-0 group-hover/link:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
            </a>
            <a
                href="https://glstudios.dev"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="group/link relative bg-zinc-800/80 backdrop-blur-sm hover:bg-zinc-700/80 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-zinc-600/50 hover:border-purple-400/60 hover:scale-105 overflow-hidden flex items-center gap-2"
            >
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover/link:text-purple-400 transition-colors" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="relative z-10 group-hover/link:text-purple-400 transition-colors">Visita la Web</span>
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-purple-500/10 opacity-0 group-hover/link:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    @keyframes pulse-slow {
        0%, 100% {
            opacity: 0.1;
        }
        50% {
            opacity: 0.15;
        }
    }

    @keyframes pulse-slower {
        0%, 100% {
            opacity: 0.1;
        }
        50% {
            opacity: 0.2;
        }
    }

    .animate-pulse-slow {
        animation: pulse-slow 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .animate-pulse-slower {
        animation: pulse-slower 6s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
</style>
